metadata.title: 2020 - Year of the Rats
metadata.name: 2020 - Year of the Rats
metadata.description: 2020 - Year of the Rats - Buffalo nickel with 24crt gold inlay. Hobo Nickel Coin hand-engraved by the Lithuanian artist Narimantas Palsis (Nari).  His signature is inscribed on each coin. This coin is limited to 1 unit.
